{"tid":1651341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"活動太亂","createTime":"2019-10-13T10:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T10:22:27.000Z","uid":238340,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2124643bdda39dd7236661e1e0ca21eb91d90df","tid":1651341,"uid":238340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"呢個星期嘅活動太多太密又太亂啦，一日成四、五個活動，又宣傳不足，好難聚人。 <br />\n<br />\n日日上連登，幾個post話突發，呢度又要人，嗰度又要人，跟本出唔切黎，又唔知去邊好。<br />\n<br />\n大家要組織返好啲，一日一個活動其實已經夠，再比多啲時間宣傳。唔係個個都睇連登，fb、Ig 同連儂牆都要有文宣。<br />\n<br />\n閒日可以係和理非活動，唱歌、人鏈、摺紙鶴都得。星期六日就搞下遊行集會。<br />\n<br />\n勇武可以不定時遊擊出動，最好做完嘢先比人發現。過程唔使比人睇，結果比人睇到已經足夠。"},{"pid":"5802834ffeff3ca7139b132e9918554dd8bc5b17","tid":1651341,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83f7e4689bc1c6c85503b99e2048fd36c0626177","tid":1651341,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"147b7bfc4092dc31aa97c2e3254a36b31399ccfa","tid":1651341,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"【和你Thank】感謝前線消防活動 #ThankYouHKFirefighters<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651243</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊感謝前線消防 屌打黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3757c0dc88132de914bd306f93e3bc725c510b","tid":1651341,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T10:22:27.000Z","msg":"有班大法師佈緊風水陣 好快贏"}]}